{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","data":{"body":"Repo change pushed as Gerrit #666 (stacked on d0e5 #665). Live-ops SEQUENCING (from plan-review advisory): the running box's fetch-secrets.sh fail-fasts on a blank autolander-gerrit-token, so the code change (#666, which removes that fetch) MUST be deployed to the host BEFORE 'terraform apply' destroys the /rebar/prod/autolander-gerrit-token SSM param — else a boot/redeploy would fail-fast. Order: (1) land #666 -> autodeploy syncs new fetch-secrets to box; (2) docker compose up -d --remove-orphans to drop the autolander+autoheal containers; remove gerrit_autolander* volumes; (3) terraform apply to destroy rebar-autolander-errors alarm + the SSM param. Bot stays PAUSED throughout (being deleted)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783991948866997001,"uuid":"034613de-4643-45ea-ad58-82449f004b44"}